NXT-64959.desc:
Issue 1: Alert icons mis alignment

User is in Item Onboarding

User creates 10-15 items and with missing mandatory information

{color:#ff5630}Then user observes alert icon is not aligned properly when we have more than 10 items which is not correct. Alert icon is showing on the Item number itself.{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: Alert icon should not show on the Item numbers, number and icon should have some space in between.{color}



Issue 2: Alert icons in all the screens are not in same size

User is in Item Onboarding

User creates 10-15 items and with missing mandatory information

{color:#ff5630}Then user observes alert icon size is different in review screens & update screens which is not correct{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: Alert icon size should be same in all the screens.{color}

