NXT-66031.desc:
For Nutrients status Icon is disappearing from Landing Page

User is in IM>Item Onboarding>Landing page>Nutrients screen

User removes mandatory information in “Update Nutrients” screen and saves the data

{color:#ff5630}Then user observes status icons disappeared from Landing page which is not correct{color}

{color:#36b37e}Expected Result: If user removes some mandatory information in any screen, status icon should show “Incomplete” icon in landing page.{color}

